com.bmwcarit.barefoot.roadmap

Class RoadMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmwcarit.barefoot.topology.Graph<Road>
      • com.bmwcarit.barefoot.roadmap.RoadMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RoadMap
extends Graph<Road>
implements Serializable
    Implementation of a road map with (directed) roads, i.e. Road objects. It provides a road network for routing that is derived from Graph and spatial search of roads with a SpatialIndex.

    Note: Since Road objects are directed representations of BaseRoad objects, identifiers have a special mapping, see Road.

    See Also:
